Eggs Benedict w/o Hollandaise, w/ unripe avocado on a cold slice of bread w/ a side of undercooked potatoes. For extra 15k I got a tiny portion of oily grilled salmon instead of smoked.
Decent coffee, but kind of bland and lacking depth.

tip.text: Great tapas, very nice place on the roof of the building. Enjoyed 'Cucurucho de Foie con Jamón', 'Panceta al Horno' and 'Croquetas de Chorizo'.
The 'GIOI Signature Crispy Duck' and stir fried mixed vegetables are excellent. 'Roast Duck Curry' is just ok. Place and service are quite nice.
Very expressive. 30 USD for egg salad croissant and tea...
